d stars and it is possible to download extra catalogues with up to 210 million stars. Stellarium has multiple sky cultures - see the constellations from the traditions of Polynesian, Inuit, Navajo, Korean, Lakota, Egyptian and Chinese astronomers, as well as the traditional Western constellations. It is also possible to visit other planets in the solar system - see what the sky looked like to the Apollo astronauts, or what the rings of Saturn looks like from Titangversionev25.2ldownload_urlxdhttps://github.com/Stellarium/stellarium/releases/download/v25.2/Stellarium-25.2-qt5-x86_64.AppImagedsizei350.02 MBhsrc_urlsüx1https://github.com/Stellarium/stellarium/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/StellariumhprovidesjstellariumglicenseühGPL-2.0+kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesćx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package«cpkgsstockstalk.appimagehpkg_namejstockstalkfpkg_idx$appimage.github.io.StockStalk.sagivodiconxåhttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io/refs/heads/master/database/icons/StockStalk/icons/512x512/stockstalk.pngkdescriptionxYour stocks on your desktopgversionfv1.0.7ldownload_urlx^https://github.com/sagivo/StockStalk/releases/download/v1.0.7/StockStalk-1.0.7-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh60.90 MBhsrc_urlsüx-https://github.com/sagivo/StockStalk/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/sagivohprovidesjstockstalkglicenseükMIT Licensekmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesćx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authentic